const content = "<div class=\"container single-page-container\">\n\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"nv-single-page-wrap col\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"nv-page-title-wrap nv-big-title\" >\n\t<div class=\"nv-page-title \">\n\t\t<small class=\"neve-breadcrumbs-wrapper\"></small>\t\t<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n</div> \n\t<div class=\"nv-content-wrap entry-content\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Who we are</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WorkSmart-AI provides AI skills training and consultancy services for organisations, particularly in education and the public sector. We are the <strong>data controller</strong> for the personal data we process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>📩 <a href=\"/contact-us/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://worksmart-ai.co.uk/contact-us/\">Contact Form</a><br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. What Information We May Collect</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We may collect and process the following types of personal data:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Identity Data</strong>: Name, job title, organisation.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Contact Data</strong>: Email address, phone number.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Professional Data</strong>: Sector, role, areas of interest (e.g. staff training needs).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Technical Data</strong>: IP address, browser type, device information, cookies.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Information about how you use our website, tools (e.g. AI Savings Calculator, Readiness Quiz), and services.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Marketing Data</strong>: Preferences for receiving newsletters, resources, or offers.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We do not knowingly collect data from children under 16.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. How We Collect Data</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We collect personal data in the following ways:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you <strong>sign up for resources or events</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you <strong>fill out a form</strong> (contact form, consultation booking).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you <strong>communicate with us</strong> (email, phone, meetings).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you <strong>use our website</strong>, through cookies and analytics tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. How We Use Your Information</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We process your data for the following purposes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>To <strong>deliver services</strong> you request (training, consultation, diagnostics).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>To <strong>respond to enquiries</strong> and communicate with you.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>To <strong>improve our services</strong> through analytics and feedback.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>To <strong>send relevant updates and resources</strong> (if you have opted in).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>To <strong>comply with legal obligations</strong> (tax, contracts, safeguarding).</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We will only use your data where we have a lawful basis (see section 5).</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We rely on one or more of the following lawful bases:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Legitimate interests</strong> – for business purposes, provided your rights are not overridden (e.g. measuring impact of services).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Consent</strong> – where you have given explicit permission (e.g. signing up to our newsletter).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Contract</strong> – to perform our agreement with you (e.g. delivering training).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Legal obligation</strong> – where we are required by law.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Sharing Your Data</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We do not sell your data. We may share data with:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Service providers</strong> (e.g. web hosting, analytics, scheduling tools like Microsoft Forms).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Professional advisers</strong> (accountants, insurers, legal advisers).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Regulators and authorities</strong> where required by law.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>All third parties are required to respect the security of your data and process it in line with GDPR.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. International Transfers</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We store data in the UK/EEA. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Data Retention</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We keep personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes collected:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Analytics data</strong>: Retained in line with provider settings (e.g. Google Analytics default).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>LMS Learning data</strong>: Data from online courses, up to 7 years after the contract ends (for legal/accounting reasons)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Client records</strong>: Up to 7 years after the contract ends (for legal/accounting reasons).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Enquiries</strong>: Up to 2 years if no contract follows.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Marketing lists</strong>: Until you unsubscribe.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Your Rights</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Under UK GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Access to your data.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Correction of inaccurate data.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Erasure of data (“right to be forgotten”).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Restriction of processing.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data portability.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Objection to processing (including direct marketing).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Withdrawal of consent at any time.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>📩 To exercise your rights, <a href=\"/contact-us/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://worksmart-ai.co.uk/contact-us/\">contact us</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are unhappy, you also have the right to complain to the <strong>ICO</strong> (<a>www.ico.org.uk</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Cookies</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience. These may include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> – required for website functionality.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> – e.g. Google Analytics, to understand website use.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Marketing cookies</strong> – only if you opt in.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can manage cookies via your browser settings. See our Cookie Policy for more detail.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">11. Data Security</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We implement technical and organisational measures to keep your data secure, including encryption, access controls, and regular review of our systems.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">12. Updates to this Policy</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on our website, with the “effective date” shown at the top.</p>\n</div>\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n</div>";
---

<LegalPage metadata={metadata} title="Privacy Policy" effectiveDate="20th October 2025" content={content} />
